                      "parameters":  {
                                         "content":  "## SOS Escritura â€” ChatBot App (FIXED v2)\n\nFluxo LINEAR â€” SEM If node:\n1. Webhook recebe POST de robot.ts (message + governance)\n2. Normalize Input: extrai channel, phone, governance.instructions_compact\n3. Load Agent Config: busca system_prompt do agents table por tenant_id\n4. Build System Message: COMBINA agent.system_prompt + governance compact\n5. AI Agent: processa com system message completo (gpt-4o-mini)\n6. Respond to Webhook (paralelo) + Save User Message â†’ Save AI Response\n\nâ•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•\nBUGS CORRIGIDOS vs. versÃ£o anterior:\nâ•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•\n1. REMOVIDO If node que descartava app_atendimento\n   â†’ O If verificava channel != app_atendimento, TRUE â†’ processava\n   â†’ Para app_atendimento (FALSE) ia para save sem AI = sem resposta!\n2. Model gpt-5-mini â†’ gpt-4o-mini (modelo real)\n3. User message era salva como type:\u0027ai\u0027 â†’ agora type:\u0027human\u0027\n4. Governance do app Ã© USADA (instructions_compact)\n   â†’ Antes: re-consultava SQL enorme (duplicaÃ§Ã£o)\n5. Agent system_prompt (da tabela agents) Ã© COMBINADO com governance\n   â†’ Antes: usava apenas governance OU apenas system_prompt\n6. REMOVIDOS: Insert rows in a table2, Execute a SQL query\n   (nodes desnecessÃ¡rios/dead-ends)\n\nâ•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•\nDepende de:\n- Agent pack SOS Escritura aplicado no tenant\n  (popula agents, agent_playbooks, rules, etc.)\n- robot.ts carrega governance e envia no body\nâ•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•"
